Milestone plan rewritten August 22 (between Milestone 1 and 2)

Milestones between 2 and 9 may be rearranged depending on whether the animator is ready earlier or 
later.

Milestone 0 
-----------
 o Minimal Interface Builder
 o No function for saving
 o No interaction with animator

Milestone 1 
-----------
 o Minimal Interface Builder
 o Able to save interfaces
 o No interaction with animator

Milestone 2
-----------
 o Minimal Interface Builder with saving
 o No interaction with animator
 o Tidied PropertiesWindow (both code and user interface)
   * Editors and Renderers for Font, Color, Border, Icon
   * Access to Bean's custom editor (if provided)

Milestone 3
-----------
 o + Simple interface generator (from ZML)

Milestone 4
-----------
 o + Example specification(s) with corresponding interface(s) and fake back-end(s).

Milestone 5
-----------
 o + Improved interface generator (from ZML) (?)

Milestone 6
-----------
 o + Interacts with animator (including history).

Milestone 7
-----------
 o + Scrolling History Animator and changes to Designer needed to accomodate this.

Milestone 8
-----------
 o Designer modified to use java.beans.EventHandler
   * Allowing any bean to be the target of an event link
 o Designer modified to use BeanContextChildComponentProxy when provided by a bean
 o Designer modified so that Form's BeanContext provides BeanContextContainerProxy
 o Tidying of designer's user interface

Milestone 9
-----------
 o + Extra plugins
   * Variants on History?
   * New beans to add to the interface

Milestone 10
------------
 o Any extra documentation needed
   * Maintainer
   * Plugin developer
   * User
